flowchart TD
    OpDB[Operational Databases\nPostgres, MySQL, Oracle] --> Extract[Extract Layer\nCDC or scheduled dump]
    SaaS[SaaS Connectors\nCRM, ERP, Ad Platforms] --> Extract
    Extract --> Staging[Staging Schema\nRaw mirror of source tables]
    Staging --> Audit[Audit Log\nRow counts, checksums]
    Staging --> Transform[Transformation Layer\ndbt models and SQL logic]
    Transform --> Clean[Clean and Deduplicate\nNull handling, dedup keys]
    Clean --> Dimensions[Dimension Tables\nCustomers, Products, Campaigns]
    Clean --> Facts[Fact Tables\nOrders, Events, Sessions]
    Dimensions --> Warehouse[Data Warehouse Serving Layer\nSnowflake, BigQuery, Redshift]
    Facts --> Warehouse
    Warehouse --> Catalog[Data Catalog\nLineage, definitions, ownership]
    Warehouse --> BI[BI Tools\nTableau, Looker, Metabase]
    Warehouse --> Notebooks[Analyst Notebooks\nJupyter, Observable]
